methods: abstract int getChildType(int groupPosition, int childPosition) Get the type of child View that will be created by getChildView(int, int, boolean, View, ViewGroup) for the specified child item.
abstract int getChildTypeCount() Returns the number of types of child Views that will be created by getChildView(int, int, boolean, View, ViewGroup) .
abstract int getGroupType(int groupPosition) Get the type of group View that will be created by getGroupView(int, boolean, View, ViewGroup) .
abstract int getGroupTypeCount() Returns the number of types of group Views that will be created by getGroupView(int, boolean, View, ViewGroup) .
